        "title": "清 劉墉 入法界體性經",
        "date": "2017/12/23",
        "category": "書法",
        "content": "<p><p>宰相劉羅鍋，是清朝「帖學派」大師。<br />請閑友們欣賞，宰相筆法周到細膩精緻迷人的小楷書，入法界體性經。<br />故宮「筆有千秋業」網站，圖片解析度很高！</p><p><a href=\"https://theme.npm.edu.tw/exh106/calligraphy10601/ch/selectionZoom/img5.html\" target=\"_blank\">https://theme.npm.edu.tw/exh106/calligraphy10601/ch/selectionZoom/img5.html</a></p><p><img src=\"./images/word_extracted/img_212538_1.jpeg\" /></p><p>局部：</p><p><img src=\"./images/word_extracted/img_212538_2.jpeg\" /></p><p><img src=\"./images/word_extracted/img_212538_3.jpeg\" /></p><p>局部：</p><p><img src=\"./images/word_extracted/img_212538_4.jpeg\" /></p><p><img src=\"./images/word_extracted/img_212538_5.jpeg\" /></p></p>"
